telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Liǎu-jiě Minecraft de jěng-tǐ shìng-néng gài-kuàng, kě-yǐ bāng-jù wǒ-men jēn-duèi gè-jǔng jī-shíng hé tsāu-tzuò-shì-tǔng tiáu-jěng yǔ yōu-huà yóu-shì.

telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: Shr̀-jiè jiā-tzài shŕ-jiān
telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Liǎu-jiě wán-jiā wán Minecraft shŕ de shì-jié (lì-rú yóu-shì mó-shr̀、kè-hù-duān huò fú-wù-duān shr̀-fǒu bèi shiū-gǎi, yǐ-jí yóu-shì bǎn-běn) yǒu-jù-yú wǒ-men tzài yóu-shì gēng-shīn shŕ jù-jùng gǎi-jìn wán-jiā tzuèi guān-shīn de bù-fen. 
Shr̀-jiè jiā-tzài shr̀-jiàn jiāng túng shr̀-jiè shiè-tzài shr̀-jiàn yī-chǐ yùng-yú jì-suàn yóu-shì huèi-huà de chŕ-shù shŕ-cháng.

Tsž shr̀-jiàn yǔ shr̀-jiè jiā-tzài shr̀-jiàn yùng-yú jì-suàn shr̀-jiè huèi-huà de chŕ-shù-shŕ-jiān. 
Chŕ-shù-shŕ-jiān (yǐ miǎu hé kè wéi dān-wèi) tzài shr̀-jiè huèi-huà jié-shù shŕ (tuèi-huéi dàu biāu-tí píng-mù, huò tsúng fú-wù-chì duàn-kāi-lián-jiē) tsè-liáng.
